<paragraph id="466E586E61EE2F51160E52D4FFA0D9D5" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BD13E82AB372A3069AED74746CD75F11" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
MEXICO. Guerrero, Mun. 
<normalizedToken id="1A9D44A87072BA3B0E19EE573A78DC03" originalValue="Mochitlán">Mochitlan</normalizedToken>
, Agua de Obispo, 
<emphasis id="2EC30B99E777FC36D1B67115B4D22E5A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">H. Kruse</emphasis>
744 (holotype MEXU00093332, isotypes CAS, ENCB, IEB).
</paragraph>
